          <h3 style='font-size:16px;'>Why does my DMCA.com Website Protection Certificate say "Account Status: Non-verified" ?</h3>
          
          <p>DMCA.com can only <b>verify</b> Website Protection Certificates of paying <a id="ctl00_cntBody_HyperLink1" title="Protection Pro" href="../ProtectionPro.aspx">Protection Pro</a> DMCA.com clients. <br><br>
</p><p><a id="ctl00_cntBody_HyperLink2" title="Upgrade" href="../Solutions/view.aspx?ID=2c98e678-a53d-4c59-bf20-05b0ad28e993&amp;r=whatisthis">Upgrade</a> to get verified:<br>
Once you upgrade your account to Protection Pro your account status will become "Verified" within 24 hours.</p><br>
<br>
<h3>Here's how to upgrade to Verified:</h3><br>
<p><b>1.</b> If you are already a DMCA.com Protection Badge user then <a id="ctl00_cntBody_HyperLink3" title="click here to login" href="../users/login.aspx">click here to login</a><br>
</p><p><b>2.</b> once logged in <a id="ctl00_cntBody_HyperLink4" title="click here to Get Verified Website Certificate" href="../toolkit/signup.aspx?lnk=1&amp;mpi=DMCA%20Toolkit">click here to Get Verified Website Certificate</a><br>
</p><p><b>Note:</b> DMCA.com uses Paypal to validate your address and other account information. </p><br>
<br>
<p>click here for new <a id="ctl00_cntBody_HyperLink5" title="Website Protection Badges and Certificates" href="../Badges.aspx">Website Protection Badges and Certificates</a><br>
</p><p>click here to <a id="ctl00_cntBody_HyperLink6" title="Get Verified Website Certificate" href="../Toolkit/Default.aspx">Get Verified Website Certificate</a></p><br>
